{"title":"霜晨书声","authors":["朱谷忠"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":1,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"霜晨书声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱谷忠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一夜飞霜，把冬天的序言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写满淡雾轻笼的村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迟出的太阳，以温热的鼻息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开始吮舔那浸人的冰凉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凸现于山坡上的一排校舍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却清晰地泼下书声琅琅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵阵，恍若升腾的炭火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把老人多年的叹息烘干"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偶然路过这里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不禁沉入春的冥想"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}